{
  "stem": "58.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Next day, a few tanks appeared at the crossing, and we threw some Molotov cocktails from the roof.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Two tanks blew up, and the Germans escaped through the hatch in fire, you know, they were wearing special suits, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the whole thing started, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took us probably, about, almost two weeks, we were fighting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One night, we actually-- the older people were sitting in a-- in a bunker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We only were fighting at night, because in the daytime we didn't have a chance, you see?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One night the sister of my uncle says she left-- she prepared for Passover and left all the food, you could use it here.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they used to make fat, you know, from chicken fat and melt it, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she had a whole pot there, like a cast iron pot, a big one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Smelts?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Hakiva Leifer, he fell on the Jordanian front in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With him, I went through, from Treblinka all the way through to the liberation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was liberated in a different place, and I, a different place-- he went, he got a passport from the [NON-ENGLISH], from another soldier that fell, a Israeli, and that's how they got him into Israel.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came out, we came out-- Hakiva Leifer and I came out in the same group from Treblinka-- that's-- this is later going on--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah I jumped ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to come to back to Hakiva Leifer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went with Hakiva Leifer to pick up this food in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was also in the underground with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a hardheaded person, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a few years, about three years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
